## 6️⃣ Edge Case Handling

Always handle unexpected inputs in functions.
This is extremely important in smart contracts!

python
def divide(a, b):
    if b == 0:
        return "Cannot divide by zero!"  # edge case handled!
    return a / b

def factorial(n):
    if n < 0:
        return "Factorial not possible for negative numbers!"
    result = 1
    for i in range(1, n + 1):
        result *= i
    return result
